@page "/"

<PageTitle>TaskManager</PageTitle>

<h1>Welcome to TaskManager</h1>

<p>This is a Blazor WebAssembly application for managing tasks and projects.</p>

<div class="alert alert-info">
    <strong>🚀 Ready for Development!</strong>
    <br>
    This application is now running as a Blazor WebAssembly client-side app,
    ready to be deployed to AWS S3 + CloudFront for static hosting.
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>Features</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Client-side Blazor WebAssembly</li>
            <li>Static hosting on S3 + CloudFront</li>
            <li>Serverless API backend</li>
            <li>PostgreSQL database</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>Architecture</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Frontend: Blazor WASM (Static)</li>
            <li>Backend: AWS Lambda (.NET 8)</li>
            <li>Database: RDS PostgreSQL</li>
            <li>CDN: CloudFront</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
